  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators study aim to evaluate the efficacy of PSU heel cushion in treatment of
      plantar fasciitis. The investigators will do a randomized controlled trial in patient with
      plantar fasciitis compared with stretching exercise alone. The outcome measurement include
      heel pain improvement, compliance, satisfaction, foot functional score at 6 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
